<H2>Stocking Up - the balanced bar</h2>

<TABLE border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <TR>
    <TD valign="top" width="142"><IMG border="0" src="/images/stocking_up/37.jpg" width="137" height="143"><BR>
      <IMG border="0" src="/images/stocking_up/38.jpg" width="140" height="143"><BR>
